WEBVTT

00:09:26.522 --> 00:09:30.672
Mainly because I'm always afraid
that nobody will ever hire me to act.

00:09:31.030 --> 00:09:32.958
AdG: That hasn't been a problem.

00:09:32.982 --> 00:09:35.410
Two Tony awards, two Golden Globes,

00:09:35.434 --> 00:09:38.007
six Emmys and two Oscar nominations.

00:09:38.535 --> 00:09:41.993
John starred in the popular sitcom
"3rd Rock from the Sun."

00:09:42.351 --> 00:09:45.828
And he recently won an Emmy
for playing Winston Churchill

00:09:45.852 --> 00:09:47.715
on the Netflix series, "The Crown."

00:09:48.029 --> 00:09:50.610
In many of your roles,
you get to invent the character,

00:09:50.634 --> 00:09:52.101
since they're not real,

00:09:52.125 --> 00:09:55.704
but here, you're playing
somebody extremely famous.

00:09:55.728 --> 00:09:57.276
So how did you get into the role

00:09:57.300 --> 00:09:59.648
and really feel what it was like
to be Churchill?